snippet.title: STEINS;GATE ELITE - 8 BIT ADV Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Play as Okabe in an 8-bit version of Akihabara in 8-BIT ADV STEINS;GATE, exclusively included with STEINS;GATE ELITE on Nintendo Switch™! The game launches on February 19, 2019 for Nintendo Switch™ so preorder today! 

Learn more about STEINS;GATE ELITE! spike-chunsoft.com/SteinsGateElite

#NintendoSwitch #SteinsGateElite
